  "text": "The development of a smart grid does not involve replacing the existing electricity network, because such a process would be impossible for technical and economical reasons. The entire concept is rather based on an enhancement of the actual network via implementing new services and features, a procedure in which the old physical infrastructure is to be maintained to the highest possible degree [CITATION_1] .",
